        <Parent_String>floors (surface elements) [300002060], floors and floor components [300052265], surface elements (architectural) [300001987], surface elements and surface element components [300078075], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
